Hola Bitcoiners! 🤩🪙✨

𝗦𝘂𝗺𝗺𝗲𝗿 𝗼𝗳 𝗕𝗶𝘁𝗰𝗼𝗶𝗻 is a global program that matches students with open source, free software and technology-related organizations, which provides mentors working on bitcoin to write code and become part of these communities while making some BTC along the way! 🌐🪙💡

Students get involved in and become familiar with the bitcoin open source community and put their summer break to good use. 🧠🔥

⚠️ 𝙀𝙡𝙞𝙜𝙞𝙗𝙞𝙡𝙞𝙩𝙮: 𝘜𝘯𝘪𝘷𝘦𝘳𝘴𝘪𝘵𝘺 𝘴𝘵𝘶𝘥𝘦𝘯𝘵𝘴 (18+) 𝘰𝘧 𝘢𝘯𝘺 𝘥𝘪𝘴𝘤𝘪𝘱𝘭𝘪𝘯𝘦.

𝗪𝗵𝗮𝘁 𝗶𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝘆𝗼𝘂?🧐
✅ Learn about bitcoin
✅ Contribute to open source
✅ Earn bitcoin
✅ Contribute to monetary revolution

